*ssnes-0.9.3 (19 Dec 2011)

  19 Dec 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> -ssnes-0.9.ebuild,
  -ssnes-0.9.1.ebuild, -ssnes-0.9.2.ebuild, +ssnes-0.9.3.ebuild:
  Bumped. Removed old versions, since upstream removed the tarballs.

*ssnes-9999 (03 Dec 2011)
*ssnes-0.9.2 (03 Dec 2011)
*ssnes-0.9.1 (03 Dec 2011)
*ssnes-0.9 (03 Dec 2011)

  03 Dec 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> +ssnes-0.9.ebuild,
  +ssnes-0.9.1.ebuild, +ssnes-0.9.2.ebuild, +ssnes-9999.ebuild,
  +files/ssnes-build.patch, +metadata.xml:
  Renamed to ssnes. Bumped and updated urls.

*SSNES-0.9.1 (31 Oct 2011)

  31 Oct 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> +SSNES-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Bumped.

*SSNES-0.9 (23 Oct 2011)

  23 Oct 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> +SSNES-0.9.ebuild,
  SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Bumped. Dropped the now redundant libsnes_path hack and python flag.

  15 Oct 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  libsamplerate was recently dropped. Updated ebuild.

  30 Sep 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-0.8.2.ebuild,
  SSNES-9999.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Added fbo flag.

  30 Sep 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-0.8.2.ebuild,
  SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Set sane defaults for libsnes_path, when using USE=dynamic.

  30 Sep 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-0.8.2.ebuild,
  SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Switched deps to virtual/libsnes.

  27 Sep 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-0.8.2.ebuild,
  SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  libsnes dep can now be satisfied by C++98 fork, which is now also used as the
  default due to not being tied down to recent GCC versions.

*SSNES-0.8.2 (27 Sep 2011)

  27 Sep 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> +SSNES-0.8.2.ebuild:
  Added regular snapshot.

  27 Sep 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Oops, forgot to add xvideo in src_configure.

  26 Sep 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Added sdl-image flag.

  24 Sep 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Fixed deps with USE=dynamic. A libsnes implementation is always required at
  runtime, but not necessarily at build time.

  23 Sep 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Added xv flag.

  22 Aug 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild,
  files/SSNES-build.patch, metadata.xml:
  Updated patch. Migrated to git-2.eclass.

  31 Mar 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Updated ffmpeg dep.

  31 Mar 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> files/SSNES-build.patch:
  Updated Makefile patch.

  27 Mar 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Removed EAPI=4 features for now.

  05 Mar 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild,
  -files/SSNES-cflags.patch:
  Dropped obsolete patch.

  10 Feb 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Made libsnes dep optional when using USE=dynamic.

  10 Feb 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Added pulseaudio to REQUIRED_USE. Added dynamic flag.

  09 Feb 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild,
  files/SSNES-build.patch:
  Updated build patch and added option to use snes9x-libsnes.

  06 Feb 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  libsamplerate is now optional.

  01 Feb 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Ported to EAPI4.

  29 Jan 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Added pulseaudio flag.

  25 Jan 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild,
  files/SSNES-build.patch, metadata.xml:
  Updated build patch. Added filters and truetype flags.

  15 Jan 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  dodoc is still non-fatal in EAPI=3.

  15 Jan 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild,
  +files/SSNES-cflags.patch:
  Fixed CFLAGS.

  15 Jan 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> files/SSNES-build.patch:
  Fixed man install path.

  15 Jan 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild:
  Forgot about prepgamesdirs. Not in the default src_install, so reverted the
  last change.

  15 Jan 2011; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> SSNES-9999.ebuild,
  +files/SSNES-build.patch:
  Patched build system and removed the kludge in src_install.

